To play note 'C' at octave 3, do the following :

Play_SB($A0, SBNotes[1]);
Play_SB($B0, SBOctaves[1 + 3 * 12]);

To shut off Adlib output, do this :

Play_SB($83, $FF);
Play_SB($B0, $11);

